    @Generated(value={"RichFaces CDK","4.5.0-SNAPSHOT"})
public class UITab
extends AbstractTab
implements javax.faces.component.behavior.ClientBehaviorHolder, AbstractTogglePanelTitledItem, AjaxProps, BypassProps, CoreProps, EventsMouseProps, I18nProps

    The <rich:tab> component represents an individual tab inside a <rich:tabPanel> component, including the tab's content. Clicking on the tab header will bring its corresponding content to the front of other tabs.

    akolonitsky
